Regressions

Distribution of outdegrees and cluster sizes at distance threshold = 0.015 by age category

  • Data are from 5 bootstrap values
  • Outliers have been censored (winsorized) to 95% range of values
Regressing age without stage interaction
m1 <- compare.reg.bs2(ls = cw_Baseline0, reg = lm, y = 'size', model = model1)

    • At threshold 0.015, neighborhood would find 23%
    • SA would find 0%
